{
  "Comment": "AFM Phase 00 — point api.aerial-fleet-monitor at the Cloudflare Tunnel. Zone is on Route 53 (Z04568022MZ21HXK15I1D); Cloudflare Tunnel terminates HTTPS and forwards to openclaw-pc. UPSERT for idempotent re-applies.",
  "Changes": [
    {
      "Action": "UPSERT",
      "ResourceRecordSet": {
